
# Recruitment Management System 

This project is an **AI-powered recruitment management system** built with **Django**, designed to automate and streamline the entire hiring workflow — from job request creation, to job posting, to candidate evaluation and scoring.

The system includes automated job offer generation, email-based candidate extraction, CV parsing using OCR + KMeans clustering, LLM-based résumé summarization, semantic embeddings, and similarity scoring between job requirements and CV content.


##  Features

###  **Authentication & Roles**

The system supports multiple user roles, each with specific permissions:

| Role                       | Permissions                                                                        |
| -------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Responsable de Service** | Creates job requests (demandes de recrutement)                                     |
| **Admin RH**               | Validates or rejects job requests; generates job offers; manages recruitment steps |
| **DG**                     | Makes final approval on job requests (accept/reject)                               |
| **Admin**                  | Full access to users, dashboard, recruitment workflow                              |

